data.description: Relocation sale- Motivated Seller! Welcome home to this beautifully updated 3/4 bedroom home in Mission Hills. The professionally remodeled kitchen (2022) offers new counter tops, cabinets, appliances, and custom tile backsplash. Enjoy a relaxing afternoon by the double sided fireplace in the sun soaked family room overlooking the large fenced back yard. The updated main floor master suite features a huge tile shower and large walk in closet. Upstairs you'll find two more generously sized bedrooms and a full bath. The finished lower level features in floor heat with a large family room , full bath with jetted tub, wet bar, and tons of storage space. Many additional updates including new window treatments throughout, new furnace in 2020 and more. Close to I94 for an easy commute!
